        "content": {
          "type": "Question",
          "version": 1,
          "locked": false,
          "questionId": "gAMi2d",
          "tiles": [
            {
              "id": "A7U_67QUw-BTHv9R",
              "title": "Question Prompt",
              "fixedPosition": true,
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<p>What do you know about insects in your state? How could you find out more. Use the questions below as a place to get started, then work with your group to develop some questions you&#x27;d like to answer about moths. Can you find and comment on some insect images? How would you contribute to these ideas if you found something new?</p>"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "ymWcoP-hTUWqoGWQ",
              "title": "Text 2",
              "content": {
                "type": "Text",
                "format": "html",
                "text": [
                  "<ol><li>How many different species (or types) of insects are there in the entire world?</li><li>How many different species of insects are there in your state?</li><li>How many different species (or types) of moths are there in the entire world?</li><li>How many different species of moths are there in your state?</li></ol>"
                ]
              }
